<Author>travelgrumpy
<Content>Nicely central For a night in Amsterdam, we dediced we wanted a cheapish hotel in the centre. After an internet search we found this hotel. We checked in, and got told that we were allowed to bring 'guests' back to the room. Kind of strange, but he ho, we are in Amsterdam. The room was very basic, and not very big. The bathroom was oke, could be better maintained. We went out in Amsterdam for the evening, and the hotel is prefectly located for this. After a basic night sleep, we had breakfast, which actually is better than the room, basic but sufficient.Checking out went without problems, all in all value for money. 
