<Content>dont do it!! do not book this hotel!!!!we reserved rooms for 11 people back in february for the weekend of 21st april for my brothers 21st birthday. we booked via a web site that was supposed to make it easy to book . we received confirmation emails to say our booking was complete. the booking agent rang us 2 days before departure to say that the hotel had cancelled the rooms due to a problem with the debit card number. i immediately phoned the hotel to sort the confusion and they told me the rooms were now cancelled and let to somebody else and they hung up on me!! the booking agent said they were not responsible for the hotels action and were unfortunately not able to find us alternative rooms. i was horrified and had to spend 8 hours on the wednesday before dpearture on the internet trying to find rooms for 11 guys for that friday. i eventually got a late cancellation at 11.30pm in a hotel 10km outside amsterdam instead of the central rooms we had booked well in advance during one of amsterdams busiest weekends of the year. the hotel managed to hang up on me and my partner and another booking agent trying to help us 4 times during the same day continually saying your rooms are cancelled. they could have ruined what should have been a fab weekend and i was simply lucky through persistence to find them alternative rooms. leave this hotel well alone. 
